346
00:36:23,358 --> 00:36:24,086
Krishna...

347
00:36:26,161 --> 00:36:27,093
I'm sorry

348
00:36:29,731 --> 00:36:31,995
I admit, I lied to you in the beginning

349
00:36:32,868 --> 00:36:33,630
But now...

350
00:36:36,805 --> 00:36:38,602
I really love you Krishna

351
00:36:38,807 --> 00:36:41,571
