419
00:41:54,422 --> 00:41:55,753
My name is Vikram Sinha

420
00:41:57,525 --> 00:41:58,423
What do you want?

421
00:41:58,927 --> 00:42:04,422
Don't go back the way you came.

422
00:42:05,400 --> 00:42:06,196
What does that mean?

423
00:42:06,401 --> 00:42:08,995
I mean, you came alone

424
00:42:09,804 --> 00:42:10,964
