425
00:42:16,878 --> 00:42:20,006
Krishna, your father, Rohit Mehra,
is still alive.

426
00:42:30,959 --> 00:42:31,823
What did you say?

427
00:42:39,334 --> 00:42:43,862
This picture was taken when
your father worked for Dr. Arya

428
00:42:44,606 --> 00:42:47,404
And I was the Senior Security
Officer at Technotronics.

429
00:42:48,543 --> 00:42:50,204
