434
00:43:03,625 --> 00:43:05,217
and the honesty in his eyes.

435
00:43:07,295 --> 00:43:08,762
He was always smiling...

436
00:43:12,834 --> 00:43:15,894
but someone cast an evil eye on him.

437
00:43:17,639 --> 00:43:18,936
It's been so many years,

438
00:43:20,575 --> 00:43:21,735
but that time...

439
