project and go back to India.

442
00:43:32,420 --> 00:43:33,478
Good morning, chief

443
00:43:34,656 --> 00:43:37,181
Mr. Vikram? Welcome!

444
00:43:37,492 --> 00:43:38,459
How are you this morning?

445
00:43:38,660 --> 00:43:40,025
