can see the future.

452
00:44:04,452 --> 00:44:06,920
Not believing does not change
the truth, Mr. Vikram.

453
00:44:07,889 --> 00:44:09,982
You will believe it, when you see it?

454
00:44:10,191 --> 00:44:12,625
What? You mean you're going to...

455
