475
00:46:46,347 --> 00:46:53,185
Now go to your Mom. My son's
coming back to me.

476
00:46:55,056 --> 00:46:59,425
Congratulations, chief! Your wife's
going to deliver a baby boy tomorrow!

477
00:46:59,761 --> 00:47:02,525
But I'm going to distribute sweets
today! In fact, right now?

478
00:47:02,730 --> 00:47:03,628
What did you say?

479
00:47:04,432 --> 00:47:05,729
What happened to my Rohit?

480
00:47:06,201 --> 00:47:07,168
What happened, Mom?

481
00:47:07,702 --> 00:47:10,500
No! That's impossible!

482
00:47:11,339 --> 00:47:12,897
My Rohit can't be dead!

483
00:47:14,242 --> 00:47:15,504
My Rohit is alive!

484
00:47:15,777 --> 00:47:16,334
No!

485
00:47:17,178 --> 00:47:17,803
No!

486
00:47:18,913 --> 00:47:19,777
Which means, I...

487
00:47:20,248 --> 00:47:24,742
Chief, the computer's malfunctioning!
Something's wrong with it!

488
00:47:52,914 --> 00:47:53,903
Dr. Arya!

489
00:47:55,416 --> 00:48:00,376
It's 6:40 there, it's 6:30 now!
This means, in just 10 minutes!

490
00:48:00,588 --> 00:48:01,555
in this very room!

491
00:48:07,295 --> 00:48:08,592
Look! Dr. Arya!

492
00:48:10,031 --> 00:48:12,556
Have you heard of Shahjahan, Doctor Mathur?

493
00:48:12,767 --> 00:48:14,632
Of course! He built the Taj Mahal.

494
00:48:14,869 --> 00:48:16,530
Incomplete knowledge is always dangerous.

495
00:48:16,871 --> 00:48:19,635
Shahjahan had the hands of workers
who built the Taj Mahal, chopped off!

496
00:48:19,841 --> 00:48:22,139
so that there would never be another Taj Mahal.

497
00:48:22,610 --> 00:48:26,046
Rohit Mehra is a worker for me
and I'm his Shahjehan.

498
00:48:27,015 --> 00:48:29,575
You mean, you're also going to
cut off Rohit's hands?

499
00:48:29,784 --> 00:48:32,685
No... his brain!

500
00:48:33,588 --> 00:48:39,185
because Rohit's brain will create problems,
for himself as well as for me.

501
00:48:40,228 --> 00:48:43,595
Actually, I'm going to feel very sorry about
it because Rohit is a very good boy.

502
00:48:43,798 --> 00:48:47,495
Sincere, honest, intelligent...

503
00:48:47,702 --> 00:48:49,966
They're coming here, chief. Please leave!

504
00:48:50,171 --> 00:48:52,696
No, no! I'm won't let this computer
go into the wrong hands.

505
00:48:52,907 --> 00:48:54,135
I'll destroy everything!

506
00:48:54,509 --> 00:48:55,032
All right!

507
00:48:55,243 --> 00:48:57,143
I'll try and stop them!

508
00:49:01,816 --> 00:49:02,441
Hello!

509
00:49:02,650 --> 00:49:03,275
Mom?

510
00:49:03,551 --> 00:49:06,452
Rohit? I've brought Nisha to the hospital.

511
00:49:06,654 --> 00:49:09,680
Congratulations! You're going to
become a father anytime.

512
00:49:09,891 --> 00:49:11,688
Come home soon, son

513
00:49:11,893 --> 00:49:14,020
I'm coming, Mom! I'm coming!

514
00:49:14,228 --> 00:49:19,461
Rohit... What's the matter? You sound tense?

515
00:49:19,901 --> 00:49:24,065
I've been exploited, the world is very selfish!

516
00:49:24,272 --> 00:49:27,867
Don't worry, I'll be back, I'll be back soon.

517
00:50:31,606 --> 00:50:32,766
Rohit!

518
00:50:34,242 --> 00:50:35,937
What have you done?

519
00:50:39,080 --> 00:50:44,040
I've destroyed your dream...
I've destroyed everything!

520
00:50:46,354 --> 00:50:48,447
because I've got to know of your intentions

521
00:50:48,790 --> 00:50:55,525
But those who know me also
know that I never accept defeat.

522
00:50:59,267 --> 00:51:01,132
I'll rebuild this computer

523
00:51:02,170 --> 00:51:04,638
using your research.

524
00:51:05,773 --> 00:51:08,742
But I don't need you anymore.

525
00:51:11,779 --> 00:51:14,543
Thank you so much for everything, Rohit

526
00:51:14,816 --> 00:51:15,646
Good bye

527
00:51:16,918 --> 00:51:17,816
Hold it, sir!

528
00:51:22,023 --> 00:51:24,253
Don't kill him, sir

529
00:51:28,329 --> 00:51:33,631
If you kill Rohit... then even if you
build the computer again

530
00:51:34,001 --> 00:51:36,561
