531
00:51:38,840 --> 00:51:41,638
You need a password to start the computer

532
00:51:42,210 --> 00:51:44,735
and the password is Rohit himself.

533
00:51:45,213 --> 00:51:45,872
What?

534
00:51:46,481 --> 00:51:47,209
Yes, sir

535
00:51:48,082 --> 00:51:49,640
I've seen it with my own eyes.

536
00:51:50,585 --> 00:51:56,023
Until scans of his retina and heartbeat
are fed into the computer...

537
00:51:56,924 --> 00:51:58,653
the computer will not start.

538
00:52:07,001 --> 00:52:08,901
This means, I'll have to keep you alive

539
00:52:09,770 --> 00:52:13,331
till I don't build a new computer.

540
00:52:17,078 --> 00:52:20,172
But die, you will.

541
00:52:21,482 --> 00:52:22,676
For the world.

542
00:52:27,388 --> 00:52:28,753
Breaking news.

543
00:52:29,156 --> 00:52:30,885
Tragedy strikes!

544
00:52:31,292 --> 00:52:34,318
Following a fire that broke out in
the lab of Technotronics...

545
00:52:34,529 --> 00:52:39,262
The famous Indian genius Rohit Mehra
has met with a tragic death.

546
00:52:40,101 --> 00:52:46,040
Let's observe a 2-minute silence,
so that Rohit Mehra's soul rests in peace.

547
00:52:57,451 --> 00:53:01,751
Ever since, I had no choice but
to work for Dr. Arya.

548
00:53:03,457 --> 00:53:05,357
I couldn't even go to the police...

549
00:53:07,795 --> 00:53:13,062
because if Dr. Arya doubted me,
he would've killed me.

550
00:53:14,569 --> 00:53:17,299
And I was the only man who could
get in touch with your family.

551
00:53:18,906 --> 00:53:22,865
That's exactly why I've been looking for your
grandma and you for so many years.

552
00:53:24,312 --> 00:53:27,008
And finally, I met you today, through Priya.

553
00:54:02,483 --> 00:54:03,643
Dr. Arya

554
00:54:08,522 --> 00:54:09,648
20 years...

555
00:54:12,827 --> 00:54:15,318
for 20 years, he's kept a
mother away from her son

556
00:54:16,664 --> 00:54:18,859
and a son away from his father

557
00:54:21,636 --> 00:54:24,002
It's because of his lies that I lost my mother.

558
00:54:33,481 --> 00:54:34,573
Where is my father?

559
00:54:34,949 --> 00:54:36,280
Here in Singapore.

560
00:54:37,051 --> 00:54:41,010
For 20 years Dr. Arya has used
machines to keep him in a state

561
00:54:41,255 --> 00:54:44,747
that only his brain is alive,
his body almost dead.

562
00:54:48,663 --> 00:54:52,326
Good evening, my friend Rohit Mehra

563
00:54:58,072 --> 00:55:00,040
How are you feeling today?

564
00:55:02,677 --> 00:55:05,976
Are these machines taking good care of you?

565
00:55:06,681 --> 00:55:07,545
Yes?

566
00:55:10,251 --> 00:55:11,183
Good!

567
00:55:12,353 --> 00:55:15,880
Tomorrow's the glorious and historic day

568
00:55:16,090 --> 00:55:24,555
when my, sorry, our computer
will be inaugurated.

569
00:55:25,366 --> 00:55:32,169
Yes! Ours, because nothing
was possible without you

570
00:55:32,373 --> 00:55:37,242
For so many years, you have
shown such patience and understanding

571
00:55:37,478 --> 00:55:39,639
and cooperated with me.

572
00:55:40,381 --> 00:55:44,977
When the computer starts tomorrow

573
00:55:47,655 --> 00:55:54,026
your utility will come to an end,
and so will your pain.

574
00:55:59,100 --> 00:56:00,567
See you tomorrow

575
00:56:10,411 --> 00:56:11,673
Breaking news!

576
00:56:13,214 --> 00:56:16,183
Dr. Arya has suddenly been
reminded of the poet Kabir.

577
00:56:16,517 --> 00:56:18,041
Do today, what you must do tomorrow...

578
00:56:18,252 --> 00:56:20,015
and do right now, what you must do today.

579
00:56:20,221 --> 00:56:26,319
That's why, Dr. Arya has decided
to start the computer today itself.

580
00:56:27,161 --> 00:56:30,426
and also end Rohit's life.

581
00:56:31,632 --> 00:56:34,567
Is this where my father is kept?

582
00:56:35,870 --> 00:56:41,240
Yes! But it's almost impossible
for a stranger to get there...

583
00:56:41,809 --> 00:56:45,643
Dr. Arya has kept very tight security
everywhere on the island

584
00:56:45,980 --> 00:56:49,416
So that now no one comes between
him and the computer

585
00:56:49,650 --> 00:56:52,949
Krishna, if Dr. Arya starts the computer

586
00:56:53,587 --> 00:57:04,987
how much havoc he can wreak and
the destruction he can cause, is unimaginable

587
00:57:06,233 --> 00:57:15,437
mine... yours... ours, the worlds
destiny will come in his clutches.

588
00:57:16,677 --> 00:57:19,475
That's why, Dr. Arya has to be
stopped at any cost.

589
00:57:20,614 --> 00:57:25,677
Now you have to save not only your father
but the whole mankind, Krishna.

590
00:57:32,026 --> 00:57:32,617
Hello.

591
00:57:32,993 --> 00:57:33,891
Krishna?

592
00:57:35,429 --> 00:57:36,293
Grandma!

593
00:57:36,897 --> 00:57:39,889
Krishna, are you okay?

594
00:57:42,169 --> 00:57:43,193
Yes, Grandma

595
00:57:43,938 --> 00:57:47,897
I don't know why I'm feeling worried.

596
00:57:48,576 --> 00:57:50,100
When are you coming back?

597
00:57:50,744 --> 00:57:52,006
Come back soon

598
00:57:53,581 --> 00:58:00,350
Your father's death anniversary is nearing,
you need to be here and fulfill the duties of a son.

599
00:58:01,889 --> 00:58:06,519
I remember, Grandma. don't worry...

600
00:58:08,929 --> 00:58:10,954
I'll fulfill all the duties of a son.

601
00:58:42,162 --> 00:58:43,789
WELCOME TO THE FUTURE

602
00:58:46,467 --> 00:58:47,729
Congratulations Sir!

603
00:58:52,406 --> 00:58:56,502
See, Rohit I've won!

604
00:58:58,946 --> 00:59:04,179
Now if you want you can end your life.

605
00:59:08,055 --> 00:59:10,546
Or do you want me to help?

606
00:59:15,095 --> 00:59:25,903
But what's the hurry? At least see how your
invention is going to make me God!

607
01:00:18,826 --> 01:00:28,292
Rohit, we built this computer
so that we can see our future

608
01:00:28,502 --> 01:00:29,992
and change it!

609
01:00:32,539 --> 01:00:38,705
I will also change my future and show you
Today itself!

610
01:00:47,621 --> 01:00:49,589
Dr. Arya's gone to look for the masked man

611
01:00:51,558 --> 01:00:52,422
Masked man?

612
01:01:14,548 --> 01:01:15,344
Kristian!

613
01:01:21,855 --> 01:01:22,617
Krishna

614
01:01:24,658 --> 01:01:25,989
Look Dr. Arya!

615
01:01:27,327 --> 01:01:28,157
Come on, let's go!

616
01:01:43,744 --> 01:01:47,009
What had Kristian done? Why kill him?

617
01:01:48,415 --> 01:01:53,079
Dr. Arya has probably started the
computer and, he must've seen...

618
01:01:53,287 --> 01:01:54,413
His future!

619
01:01:56,056 --> 01:02:01,653
It will be just as Dr. Arya has seen.

620
01:08:20,540 --> 01:08:23,805
I've changed my future!
I've changed my tomorrow!

621
01:08:24,010 --> 01:08:25,944
There is no mask any longer...

622
01:08:26,146 --> 01:08:32,381
Henceforth the new face of God is...
Dr. Siddhant Arya!

623
01:08:46,867 --> 01:08:49,131
How is this possible?

624
01:08:50,437 --> 01:08:55,739
I've killed him with my own hands.
Then... who's this?

625
01:08:57,043 --> 01:09:01,742
Its 9:15 there and it's 9 here.

626
01:09:02,949 --> 01:09:05,417
This means, he'll be here in
the next 15 minutes.

627
01:09:06,019 --> 01:09:08,988
that means he is already on the island!

628
01:09:25,872 --> 01:09:26,531
Stop!

629
01:09:30,810 --> 01:09:37,181
To capture him we need
planning not power.

630
01:10:30,437 --> 01:10:34,430
Dr. Arya has kept very tight security
everywhere on the island.

631
01:11:03,403 --> 01:11:09,308
You're good! Very good.
But I'm better

632
01:11:16,816 --> 01:11:19,876
Yes, I am better

633
01:11:21,421 --> 01:11:24,390
Because I have seen the future.

634
01:11:30,063 --> 01:11:35,592
But due to lack of time what I
couldn't see is what I want to know...

635
01:11:37,704 --> 01:11:39,535
Why do you want to kill me?

636
01:11:41,908 --> 01:11:45,400
And why do you want to rescue Rohit Mehra?

637
01:11:51,518 --> 01:11:52,746
Who are you?

638
01:11:54,187 --> 01:11:58,317
Come to me and give me the answer.

639
01:11:59,192 --> 01:11:59,954
come!

640
01:12:12,472 --> 01:12:15,703
I've told you, I have seen the future

641
01:12:16,242 --> 01:12:20,576
And I know who is with me...

642
01:12:21,581 --> 01:12:22,445
Hello!

643
01:12:23,149 --> 01:12:25,117
and who is against me

644
01:12:26,386 --> 01:12:28,650
So... please cooperate

645
01:13:31,251 --> 01:13:32,411
Who are you?

646
01:13:35,255 --> 01:13:37,086
We'll get to know right now.

647
01:15:42,515 --> 01:15:45,313
Who... are you?

648
01:16:07,273 --> 01:16:09,969
Your son... Krishna!

649
01:17:19,245 --> 01:17:19,973
Mom.

650
01:18:57,009 --> 01:18:58,237
Thank you, Jadoo.

651
01:19:00,346 --> 01:19:01,335
Thank you

